{"tid":1051880,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓文「Sorry囉」應該要點講？　IZ*ONE本田仁美話你知","createTime":"2019-03-08T02:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T18:35:20.000Z","uid":238483,"like":34,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4e632da3b741fecd5044603bc34ee07f29837613","tid":1051880,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2516677/org/ca6ce55032a8746441120f5f2d9bc5a2.jpg/HxEyBj7wCK4fRTr2E9NgAnpYj8HdiWkvvGxHeLxsR3g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2516677%2Forg%2Fca6ce55032a8746441120f5f2d9bc5a2.jpg%2FHxEyBj7wCK4fRTr2E9NgAnpYj8HdiWkvvGxHeLxsR3g&h=f52f7a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人最忌道歉時說「對唔住囉」、「Sorry囉」，讓人覺得該道歉不夠真誠，態度欠佳。原來最近韓國新興的網絡用語中，也有類似「對唔住囉」、「Sorry囉」的句子，就是「지송지송」，而將這句話發揚光大的竟是日本女團AKB48出身，現任韓團IZ*ONE成員本田仁美。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2516634/org/7bc196f5047efd09cbc5376e7be76b28.JPG/hYwMJb7LMv-YoZyhfpkWYW9ATQ_f3F4l106owddOqME\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2516634%2Forg%2F7bc196f5047efd09cbc5376e7be76b28.JPG%2FhYwMJb7LMv-YoZyhfpkWYW9ATQ_f3F4l106owddOqME&h=2a8de1c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本田仁美外表趣緻可愛，不過毒舌技能同樣非常厲害。（網上圖片）<br />\n「지송지송」發音類似「智鬆智鬆」，源於韓文「對不起」（죄송），雖然意思類似「對唔住囉」和「Sorry囉」，不過語氣相對而言較為「對唔住囉」和「Sorry囉」 調皮可愛，是最近韓國流行的網絡交流用語。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2516632/org/624b85a83309fe6e49c494ccaa05afb9.JPG/x76udATvudy0VvsdXhJn0k6B9g7pZHzAyo-fPcqPnz0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2516632%2Forg%2F624b85a83309fe6e49c494ccaa05afb9.JPG%2Fx76udATvudy0VvsdXhJn0k6B9g7pZHzAyo-fPcqPnz0&h=936cbea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓本田仁美認識「지송지송」一詞的原來是IZ*ONE成員金采源（左）。（網上圖片）<br />\n至於本田仁美是如何將「지송지송」發揚光大呢？事緣本田仁美與IZ*ONE隊友金采源在一月同遊南山塔，並為WIZ*ONE（IZ*ONE粉絲）進行直播，期間金采源教導本田仁美「지송지송」一詞，又示範使用「지송지송」一詞時，表情應略顯輕挑，向來在AKB48以毒舌見稱的本田仁美當然能迅速掌握，其後更被隊友李彩演大爆常用「지송지송」與隊友曹柔理吵架，因而成為WIZ*ONE和K-pop迷的熱話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Du6veg_VYAAUcWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDu6veg_VYAAUcWz.jpg&h=889ce2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/ws/304/amz/worldservice/live/assets/images/2013/09/12/130912151728_blobfish_512x288_greenpeace_nocredit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fws%2F304%2Famz%2Fworldservice%2Flive%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F2013%2F09%2F12%2F130912151728_blobfish_512x288_greenpeace_nocredit.jpg&h=599758dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.91toy.com.tw/img/product_pic/2017112115280700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.91toy.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fproduct_pic%2F2017112115280700.jpg&h=daf9dd22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可愛隊友曹柔理"},{"pid":"db50a73039a546f49a7eac05944eec236d27b868","tid":1051880,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a885c23c029f824f2865059f233dff16e9b6e4e4","tid":1051880,"uid":555,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:42:49.000Z","msg":"邊能到趣緻可愛"},{"pid":"2bd677aafe362d4c5cb42c8cedc264ea9da0557b","tid":1051880,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db50a73039a546f49a7eac05944eec236d27b868","tid":1051880,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"竟然無錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f2c6ee1fccee3e01c46bb3b9e77985179bc138","tid":1051880,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a885c23c029f824f2865059f233dff16e9b6e4e4","tid":1051880,"uid":555,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:42:49.000Z","msg":"邊能到趣緻可愛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:47:56.000Z","